<i>noun</i>: 첨예화 [처몌화], 증폭 [증폭], 격화 [겨콰], 강화 [강화] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>첨예화 [처몌화]</dt><br>
<dd>intensification</dd><br>
<dd>상황이나 사태가 날카롭고 거세게 됨. 또는 그렇게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of a situation or matter becoming acute and violent, or an action of making something acute and violent.</dd><br>
<dt>증폭 [증폭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. intensification; increase</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 어떤 일의 범위를 넓혀서 크게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of increasing the scope of an idea or project.</dd><br>
<dd>2. amplification</dd><br>
<dd>빛, 전류, 음향 등의 진폭을 늘림.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of increasing the amplitude of light, electricity, sound, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>격화 [겨콰]</dt><br>
<dd>intensification; aggravation</dd><br>
<dd>감정이나 행동 등이 지나치게 급하고 거세짐.</dd><br>
<dd>The state in which an emotion or behavior becomes overly hasty and tough.</dd><br>
<dt>강화 [강화]</dt><br>
<dd>1. reinforcement; strengthening</dd><br>
<dd>세력이나 힘을 더 강하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of causing power or force to be stronger.</dd><br>
<dd>2. reinforcement; tightening; intensification</dd><br>
<dd>수준이나 정도를 높임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of causing a level or degree to be higher.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>